>\n因為本身冇做開運動<br />\n但讀大學𠴱陣迷上咗行山<br />\n係行1x個鐘𠴱隻<br />\n搞到傷膝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n骨科醫生都話救唔到<br />\n話葡萄糖胺都係呃吓自己咁<br />\n物理治療師話只能夠練吓肌肉等佢退化得慢啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw我識有位嬸嬸係50歲左右<br />\n佢都係行山行到傷膝<br />\n跟住唔知喺邊度<br />\n打啲嘢入膝頭<br />\n佢話好咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係咪樓上講嘅透明質酸"},{"pid":"35440c691dc8ea95145bf298bc9be0c64215904d","tid":2227534,"uid":206168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T20:18:24.000Z","msg":"好耐之前仆街 最近個膝一伸直就會啪聲 而且禁落去捽個膝頭會痛 我係咪都退化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申冇咩做運動"},{"pid":"1eabe9a43e4c2680f05c496b86c766c570d6f48a","tid":2227534,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"未到30歲<br />\n<br />\n腳踝成日傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369c8f60a6e6c76f42c4a7082b64181379898813","tid":2227534,"uid":205037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"巴打可以試下關節寶保養品，因為我爸爸中年都試過有咁嘅問題，佢食咗之後都好左好多"},{"pid":"76a92498d798d68c2f13576294beceb1823ef178","tid":2227534,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"成日跑步踩單車係咪唔好"},{"pid":"0b347b1fe6b0099221eed1392ae90efde7bc6e60","tid":2227534,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59525ed944162a5e194e4b3f90dc3281fc12488a","tid":2227534,"uid":153258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b5deae43e9aab7f009422c32797f56957d15d1","tid":2227534,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"396c1c8084756cc0cfe9bed1916a285e053f340d","tid":2227534,"uid":691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"有冇的起心肝去練大脾肌肉？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T22:39:06.000Z","msg":"唔練就陰陰痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n練完第二日劇痛<br />\n<br />\n都唔知練唔練好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim